org.jboss.windup.reporting.pegdown

Class WindupCodeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pegdown.ast.AbstractNode
      • org.jboss.windup.reporting.pegdown.WindupCodeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.parboiled.trees.GraphNode<org.pegdown.ast.Node>, org.pegdown.ast.Node

    public class WindupCodeNode
extends org.pegdown.ast.AbstractNode
    Provides an object that is similar to a CodeNode, but that also contains a code type attribute.
    NOTE: It does not appear that the serializer will work if this actually subclasses CodeNode, so this is directly a subclass of AbstractNode.
